Description: Image processing application based on the OTB library
 Monteverdi 2 is an image processing application based on the OTB library. It
 takes advantage of the streaming and multi-threading capabilities of the OTB
 pipeline. It also uses cool features as processing on demand and automagic
 file format I/O. Monteverdi 2 is distributed under the free software license
 CeCILL (similar to GNU GPL) to encourage contribution from users and to
 promote reproducible research.
